   <!-- TOWRdocs Header
        Imagery style rules for pointset plugin products.
   -->
   <!-- TOWRdocs Description
        This file sets pointset plugin style rules, including display parameters, legends, and units. It
        is an update to the baseline file, and is currently used to set select AMSR2, SAR, ATMS, and GPM  parameters.  
    This file has the following changes/additions: 

        Wind speeds are changed from m/s in the base to knots, 
        and the range from 0-75 m/s to 0-150 kt, increments in 20

        SST, CLW, TPW, Rain Rate rules were added
        by SpORT EPDT (Dec 1-3 2015)

        Modifed colormaps to point to those for GOES-R in this repo for
        RR, TPW, SST.

        creatingEntity entries match those of the the NetCDF file attribute
        instrument_name, and correspond to the Pacific, CONUS, Alaska, Puerto
        Rico regions.

        Precipitation increments are changed to inches/hour, consistent w/GOES-R baseline
        RRQPE product in the goes-r wfo collection.

        Added style rules for GMI Imagery CH 06-09.
        Added style rules Jason-2 wave heights in the case the pointset plugin is used.

	Added colormap for MW imagery 36.5 and 89GHz, contributed by SpORT 18 Apr 2016

         The color map for TPW has two options, color-pw10-10, and color-pw8-10.  The latter is commented
         out, currently.
         Contributors: Tim Schmit and Jordan Gerth
        
		9 Sep 2016 adds ATMS SIce, TSkin, SWE
		3 Oct 2016 modifies TPW range, consistent w/that of other TPW products

        Many style rules that are commented out have been tested but are not currently
        implemented in this collection for that particular product.  

        See the netcdfGrid style rules for the IMERG product.
    
        Restart CAVE whenever making changes to this file. 

   -->
    <!-- 
        This is an incremental override file, indicating that the files
        at different localization levels will be combined. 
    -->
   <!-- TOWRdocs Status
    This file is a modification to the baseline pointset imagery style rule file of the same 
    name, to include updated colormaps, units, and display ranges.

	Updated ATMS rain rate parameter, avoids conflict with radar reflectivity (RR) derivedParameter
	in the baseline for radar data.
       
       Added Ice Concentration, Ice Map from NPP JRR product 9/16/2019
       1/16/2020 Update path to MW_Imagery. Add snow fall rate for ATMS
       1/20/2020 Use SICP, update displayUnits for ATMS Ice Concentration
       2/6/2020 added ATMS SNOW
       3/2/2020 Updated AMSR2 MW MBT colormaps
       5/7/2021 moves Beaufort_Wind cmap to Sat/MW/
       9/28/2021 moves Beaufort_Wind cmap to Sat/ to match base
   -->
   <!-- TOWRdocs POC
        Lee Byerle 9/28/2021
   -->
<styleRuleset>
  <styleRule>
    <paramLevelMatches>
      <creatingEntity>RADARSAT-2</creatingEntity>
      <creatingEntity>SENTINEL-1A</creatingEntity>
      <creatingEntity>AMSR2</creatingEntity>
      <parameter>WS</parameter>
    </paramLevelMatches>
    <imageStyle>
      <displayUnits>kts</displayUnits>
      <displayFlags>NoPlane</displayFlags>
      <range scale="LINEAR">
        <minValue>0</minValue>
        <maxValue>125</maxValue>
      </range>
      <defaultColormap>Sat/Beaufort_Winds</defaultColormap>
      <colorbarLabeling>
        <values>7 11 17 22 28 34 41 48 56 64</values>
      </colorbarLabeling>
    </imageStyle>
  </styleRule>
